             was indicted for <rs id="t18161030-36-off176" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18161030-36-off176" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18161030-36-off176" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
               feloniously assaulting 
                     
                        <persName id="t18161030-36-victim372" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Spicer
                        <interp inst="t18161030-36-victim372" type="surname" value="Spicer"></interp>
